tyle=\"color: red;\">所以今次不合作運動 就算面對幾大壓力都好 都要繼續落去</span><br />\n當其他香港市民認識到 我地絕對唔會作出退讓(蒙起對眼) 佢地就會將壓力轉移番去政府到<br />\n今日番到公司 都聽到有D啊姐係度屌林鄭點解唔直接出黎 撤回了左件事就算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以<br />\n怯，你就輸成世!</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"重點有足夠威攝力 ge signalling"},{"pid":"667c2f4ef6bc0b2be4449359ac2b2ba6b8f17dae","tid":1387352,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:55:35.000Z","msg":"升級"},{"pid":"dd4b8ae4f446db5c328f9131453dd79fc160411e","tid":1387352,"uid":61755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:56:23.000Z","msg":"但我覺得前線手足可以禮貌D<br />\n我今日係現場都聽見屌人影相 都覺得有D惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0252925f0dfa96b08781bcef8df45b777ef15f22","tid":1387352,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1GyfNx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1GyfNx.png&h=9796f2bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73c6764ee4c3c73f5f0713c0d5f9692eb49f2c74","tid":1387352,"uid":61755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXs9yk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXs9yk2.png&h=4fd050f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31610a421ada3e5b1f29668127ef2f4e8d10a251","tid":1387352,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bd9282609a7b54beac1e0e7b1a3b2faf1454218","tid":1387352,"uid":121058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd4b8ae4f446db5c328f9131453dd79fc160411e","tid":1387352,"uid":61755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:56:23.000Z","msg":"但我覺得前線手足可以禮貌D<br />\n我今日係現場都